Source: stlencoders
Section: libs
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Thomas Kemmer <tkemmer@computer.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 8)
Build-Depends-Indep: doxygen
Standards-Version: 3.7.3
Homepage: https://github.com/stlencoders/stlencoders

Package: libstlencoders-bin
Section: utils
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Generic Base16/Base32/Base64 encoding and decoding tools
 This package contains example programs for the stlencoders library,
 which may also be useful in their own rights.

Package: libstlencoders-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Generic Base16/Base32/Base64 encoding algorithms for C++ [development]
 This package contains the header files needed to compile programs
 which use the stlencoders library.

Package: libstlencoders-doc
Section: doc
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: stlencoders-dev
Description: Generic Base16/Base32/Base64 encoding algorithms for C++ [documentation]
 This package contains the documentation for the stlencoders library.
